==German==
===Etymology===
Old High German ''[[dese]]'', akin to Old Saxon *''these''
===Adjective===
'''diese''' (''dieser'')

# [[this]]
# [[these]]

===Usage===
* ''Ich will diese Frau'' - I want this woman.
* ''Diese Dinge sind dumm'' - These things are stupid.

